<li>What is the measure of each angle in a regular pentagon?  Explain how you know you are right.<br /></li>
<li>What is the measure of each angle in a regular hexagon?  Explain how you know you are right.<br /></li>
<li>What is the measure of each angle in a regular <m>n</m>-gon?  Explain how you know you are right.<br /></li>
 </ol>  </statement>
